name: TheSportsDB
description: Provides Formula 1 metadata for seasons, races, teams, and drivers using TheSportsDB.com API. Supports organizing F1 race recordings with detailed metadata including race results, team information, and driver data.
overview: Formula 1 metadata provider using TheSportsDB API

versions.changelog:
Initial release with F1 metadata support
- Episode (race) metadata provider
- Series (season) metadata provider
- Image provider for posters and fanart
- Rate limiting and caching
- Configurable API settings
